.github-upload/
_upload_git/

# Per-locale build output regenerates on every `npm run build` and is huge
# (~20k lines each); public/data.json (the pre-existing single-locale
# artifact) stays tracked per this repo's existing convention, but tracking
# these two as well would make every content-translation commit's diff
# unreviewable.
public/data.en.json
public/data.ru.json
dist/public/data.en.json
dist/public/data.ru.json
